{"tid":1979767,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"專業清算師要大家幫手清算藍屍陳文慧","createTime":"2020-04-19T15:53:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T17:26:21.000Z","uid":252031,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"69b641570be08931b6326b003438c377b4ab6faf","tid":1979767,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T15:53:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HGMMe4P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHGMMe4P.png&h=38188d28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前立法會議員區諾軒「大聲公襲警」被判罪成，案件的外判主控官大律師陳文慧（Vivien Chan）同名同樣的 Facebook 帳戶，過去曾公開批評示威者是「畜牲」、「黃屍曱甴」，形容法官是「人渣垃圾」。<br />\n<br />\n早幾日專業清算師提出咗公開信質疑佢作為大律師嘅專業操守甚至佢嘅專業資格<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gAFJhiR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgAFJhiR.png&h=6f6205ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J23iQEE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ23iQEE.png&h=3708e236&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZsW8trk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZsW8trk.png&h=ac1dd60c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳文慧現時在軒利大律師辦事處私人執業，該辦事處今（19日）發聲明指，辦事處個別成員的立場及言論，並不代表本辦事處或其他成員的立場，個別成員須為其個人行為及決定自行負責並承擔一切後果。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A4%96%E5%88%A4%E4%B8%BB%E6%8E%A7%E5%AE%98%E5%90%8C%E5%90%8D-fb-%E8%BE%B1%E7%BD%B5%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98-%E8%BB%92%E5%88%A9%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E8%A1%8C%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E%E5%89%B2%E5%B8%AD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%2588%25A4%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%2590%258D-fb-%25E8%25BE%25B1%25E7%25BD%25B5%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E8%25BB%2592%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%2589%25B2%25E5%25B8%25AD%2F&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWkigq9hDTRyGE5nekVWm24Q%3D&h=e36bff47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%2588%25A4%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%2590%258D-fb-%25E8%25BE%25B1%25E7%25BD%25B5%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E8%25BB%2592%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%2589%25B2%25E5%25B8%25AD%2F&h=229b2376\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A4%96%E5%88%A4%E4%B8%BB%E6%8E%A7%E5%AE%98%E5%90%8C%E5%90%8D-fb-%E8%BE%B1%E7%BD%B5%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98-%E8%BB%92%E5%88%A9%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E8%A1%8C%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E%E5%89%B2%E5%B8%AD/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">資料from 專業清算師fb page</span><br />\n<br />\n就軒利大律師辦事處圖與陳文慧女士撇清關係(又稱「割蓆」)的公開聲明，清算師團隊未能接受。<br />\n<br />\n蘇軾有云︰「物必先腐也，而後蟲生之」。回歸以來，當權者一直以法治之名打壓人權自由，一次又一次的釋法、政治檢控、濫捕，以至昨日(18/4)港共政權為了當中聯辦的應聲蟲，推翻多年來對基本法第22條的固有立場，一切一切均是法律制度徹底崩壞的實證。法律制度被破壞，造就法律界群魔亂舞，社會充斥以「法律界精英」之名招搖撞騙的妖怪，以似是而非的歪理扭曲法律精神，作為同業的諸位責無旁貸。<br />\n<br />\n法律界是榮辱與共的專業，當諸位選擇縱容老鼠屎為所欲為，而不加以鞭撻和譴責，最後只會身受其害。與專業資格被廣泛質疑的人於同一辦事處行事亦難免讓人有同流合污的錯覺，吾等只能奉勸各位及早與制度暴力割席。<br />\n<br />\n  貴辦事處於聲明中援引了不少Code of Conduct的條文，吾等欲以Code of Conduct的第1.1條作結；第1.1條(Respect for and upholding the rule of law and for the freedom of the individual citizen depend to a large extent on the maintenance of high standards by all who practise in the Courts)清楚說明捍衛法治和人權是大律師最重要的責任。當法治再不能保障人民的權利自由，公眾對法治信心盡失， 貴專業的glamour也終將燃燒殆盡。<br />\n<br />\n第一擊(手足只需繼續幫手Share出去)<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=244509196923191&amp;id=107843517256427\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D244509196923191%26id%3D107843517256427&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWkigq9hDTRyGE5nekVWm24Q%3D&h=9d7e2689\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=244509196923191&amp;id=107843517256427</a><br />\n<br />\n第二擊(手足盡可能Share出去外國傳媒)<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=244986670208777&amp;id=107843517256427\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D244986670208777%26id%3D107843517256427&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWkigq9hDTRyGE5nekVWm24Q%3D&h=c3aa7451\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=244986670208777&amp;id=107843517256427</a><br />\n<br />\n第三擊(不日放映敬請留意)"},{"pid":"7c444edee5174281e36abbd95c9c0481c28c64dc","tid":1979767,"uid":252031,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T15:57:53.000Z","msg":"手足任務：<br />\n(1) Tag哂全港所有傳媒＋海外傳媒<br />\n(2) 轉載公開信截圖到Twitter，Tag哂英國國會議員"},{"pid":"23d1d5915838d94ab5019eeaa30cbf5f3538b456","tid":1979767,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T16:00:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a59b3bb4492a052af71941cb8a2167a006938c62","tid":1979767,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T16:01:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"59fb4e03f02f40acee28e4563cf6f039a07f98a2","tid":1979767,"uid":229920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T16:01:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c798ddf63bad1f31bbc949f3448a8a1915f932f","tid":1979767,"uid":57309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T16:01:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5fbb4aa01afde91af29db125c9590fe750137af","tid":1979767,"uid":229920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T16:01:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9d0d755b0609524f5378d0769c3d60cf061bc5b","tid":1979767,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T16:02:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38ab473310d1d4a09f0c4bd34cd8b19c91e8c070","tid":1979767,"uid":63117,"like":